    "The keywords were slightly adjusted in different database searches to optimize the retrieval of results, and the specific search terms are presented as indicated in Table 1.",
    "To further refine the search results, certain constraints were applied: Articles needed to be in English and published within the last five years, spanning from 2019 to 2023.",
